name: miniProXL Vent Kit for all Smartphones
description:
Drive safe and legal with the miniPro Window/Dashboard Kit. As the smallest iBOLT holder, the miniPro is compatible with all case/phone combinations and is designed for easy, one-handed operation. It can be placed on the dashboard or windshield securely with the ROK II Suction Mount.

The miniPro fits phone/case combinations from 2.25 In (58mm) to 3.7 In (94mm) wide, and unlimited height. This includes phones ranging in size from an iPhone 4/4s to a Samsung Galaxy Note 3 with large case. The ROK II suction Mount has a suction cup with an sticky bottom, allowing attachment directly to any windshield or hard surface on the dashboard.
short_description: The miniProXL Vent is a universal car holder that easily clips securely onto your vehicles air vent. Vent clip rotates to your air vent blade orientation and the resting leg supports phones and case combinations of all sizes. Includes 2 different mounting options to fit you needs. Attach the mount directly to your dashboard using our adhesive miniBall mount.

name: xProDock for HTC w. 6ft USB charging cable
description:
Drive safe and legal with the xProDock. The stylish xProDock is compatible with most HTC Smartphones. The xProDock can be placed on the dashboard or windshield securely with the ROK II Suction Mount. The open design allows for buttons, cameras, and charging ports to be open and accessible. A charging arm is included that launches the iBOLT Dock'n Drive app that is free in the Google Playstore.

The xProDock fits cases and batteries that range from 2.59 In (66mm) to 3.7 In (94mm) in width, and unlimited height. This includes large cases and batteries such as Otterbox, Lifeproof, and ZeroLemon. The ROK II suction Mount has a suction cup with a sticky bottom, allowing attachment directly to any windshield or hard surface on the dashboard. A microUSB Charging cable and a dash disc for soft dashboard surfaces is also included in the kit.
short_description: The xProDock is compatible with HTC devices from the size of the One X to the One Max, and can be mounted on the dashboard or windshield. The open design allows for buttons, cameras, and charging ports to be open and accessible. The included 6ft cable allows for placement on the left side of the steering wheel.

name: Amps Plate
description: The iBOLT Amps plate is developed for users that prefer to have the car-dock attached to a pedestal Mount or vehicle specific mounting solutions from providers like KUDA, ProClip, ProFit etc. The ball joint attaches to the back of any iBOLT designed car-dock and the flat 'plate' screws into the mounting solution. The 4 holes are spaced with the industry standard 32 mm x 38 mm spacing, commonly referred to as 'AMPS' plate. Delivered with double sided tape and 4 small screws with matching small bolts. Allows car-dock to turn either horizontal or vertical. Easy to adjust while driving!
short_description: Mounting solution includes Amps mount, 2-sided tape, and screws to mount to vehicle specific mounting solutions. The 4 holes are spaced with the industry standard 32mm x 38mm spacing, commonly referred to as 'AMPS' plate.
meta_title: Amps Plate | iBOLT Car Docks | Phone Mounts Android NFC Holders
meta_description: With the iBOLT Amps you can attach your car dock to a pedestal mount or vehicle specific solutions from providers like KUDA, ProClip, ProFit etc.
more_product_info:
• 17 mm ball joint - fits all iBOLT car-docks
  • 32x38 mm industry standard hole pattern (=AMPS)
  • Use as alternative to suction mount
  • Perfect for KUDA, ProClip or any Pedestal type Mount
  • Double sided tape included and 4 screws

name: sPro2 Connect for NFC enabled Phones
description:
The sPro2 is compatible with all case/phone combinations and is designed for easy, one-handed operation. It can be placed on the dashboard or windshield securely with the ROK II Suction Mount. Designed with the iPhone in mind, the bottom feet on the sPro2 are adjustable to allow for charging and auxiliary cables. Included in the kit is an NFC tag for compatible Android phones. Using NFC Technology, the tag automatically launches the iBOLT Dock'n Drive app that can be downloaded for free in the Google Playstore. A dash disc is included for soft dashboard surfaces.

The sPro2 fits phones from 4.5 In (115mm) to 6.7 In (170mm) in height, and unlimited width. This includes phones ranging in size from an iPhone 4/4s to a Samsung Galaxy Note 3 with large case. The NFC Tag is compatible with most NFC capable Android phones.

name: Tripod miniPro + BT Selfie
description: The legs of the tripod can easily wrap around tree branches and fences. The legs are sturdy, but bendable.
short_description:
Capture the moment anywhere, anytime with the Tripod miniPro from iBOLT. One Product covers all your needs because it works with Smartphones, Digital cameras, and GoPros. This kit includes a Bluetooth Selfie camera shutter button, which lets you capture your moment at a distance up to 30 feet away. The Tripod miniPro has a flexible design which allows you to stand, bend, or wrap the tripod legs.

This kit also includes a High quality miniPro universal phone holder which works with phones from an iPhone 4 to a Samsung Galaxy note 4, and a easy to use GoPro adapter that works with all GoPros. Its portable and universal design helps you capture every moment wherever you go.
meta_title: Tripod miniPro + BT Selfie | iBOLT Car Docks | Android Mounts
meta_description: The Tripod miniPro has a flexible design which allows you to stand, bend, or wrap the tripod legs.
more_product_info:
• Comes with Bluetooth Selfie Remote for taking pictures and videos from a distance
  • Comes with a GoPro Adaptor
  • Legs are sturdy and bendable, so that you can wrap them around objects or stand the tripod upright.
